Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.78,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He never fails to surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:14.95,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I first saw his skating,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:18.06,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,it's been an unending chain of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:53.75,Grand Prix,Sign 152,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1170,1)}Sochi Grand Prix Final
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:56.45,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}He's also crushed the free skating event!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:59.76,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,It will be the fifth consecutive Grand \NPrix Final victory for Russia's legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:01.60,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Victor Nikiforov.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.94,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Nikiforov is now 27 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:07.34,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Some speculated that he \Nmight retire this season,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:11.15,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,but his masterful performance seems \Nto lay such rumors to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:15.96,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,As for Katsuki Yuri, who earned a spot \Nin the Grand Prix for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.47,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,what do you think, Honda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:20.66,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he didn't perform like \Nhis usual self today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.67,Phone,Sign 0218,0000,0000,0000,,Men's Figure Skating: Katsuki Suffers Utter Defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:20.66,Phone,Sign 0219,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HB17F42&}Katsuki Defeated: Still Needs to Work on Nerves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.07,Default,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, don't look at the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:24.14,Default,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:28.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,"Katsuki Fell to Last Place. \NIs This Season His Last?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:29.53,Default,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.44,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Katsuki Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:35.77,Phone,Sign 0236,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H575614&\an7}Top Certified Athletes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:37.70,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the dime-a-dozen top \Nfigure skaters certified by the JSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:38.83,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:40.19,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,My name makes me sound strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.24,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I finished last at my first Grand Prix Final.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:44.26,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't accept what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.26,Last,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Last Place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.44,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I even moved to a training facility in Detroit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:49.56,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and worked hard to make it to the final.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:53.17,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But the pressure had me binge-eating before \Nthe match, and our family dog died...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.57,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Mentally and physically, I was at my worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:58.07,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It was supposed to be my big day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.82,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's all my fault, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:03.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.70,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, were you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:09.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were watching on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:12.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A public viewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:21.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:22.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:43.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.61,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Junior Grand Prix Final gold medalist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.93,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri Plisetsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.71,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The "Russian Punk"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.59,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,is looking at me like I'm a piece of trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:03:59.34,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.34,Default,YP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:02.97,Default,YP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm competing in the senior division next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.84,Default,YP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need two Yuris in the same bracket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.22,Default,YP,0000,0000,0000,,Incompetents like you should \Njust retire already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.17,Default,YP,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:20.94,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I left the sport,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.49,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,there'd be tons of talented young \Nskaters rising through the ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.12,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.81,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Newscaster Morooka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.66,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.00,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early for you to retire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:38.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I've made a decision. \NPlease don't make assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.26,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do after you \Ngraduate from college?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:42.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.53,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Will you still train in Detroit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:47.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be talking that over with Coach Celestino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.01,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.51,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm asking how {\i1}you{\i0} feel about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:50.90,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to think right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.47,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Will you keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.02,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Vicchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:53.71,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Maybe just part-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:56.02,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You'll still have a chance back in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.45,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I can't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.03,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.26,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,About your free performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:00.96,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,the step sequence could use more—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.03,Default,YP,0000,0000,0000,,I won, so who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.25,Default,YP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Quit nagging, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.03,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Yuri on the Russian team...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.45,Default,Jakov,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:11.29,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If I do have a chance, someday I'd like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:11.29,Default,Jakov,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You can't talk that way forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:13.91,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,A commemorative photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.08,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:20.70,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.21,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want a photo with Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.44,Default,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.59,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This is humiliating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:29.68,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was an idiot for thinking \NI could finally meet my idol
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.80,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,on the same playing field...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:38.98,Title,Sign 0536,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}First Skate \N{\fs20}Easy as Pirozhki!! \NThe Grand Prix Final of Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Easy as Pirozhki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.30,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Prix Final of Tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:43.11,Phone,Sign 0540,0000,0000,0000,,Hasetsu Station
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:43.11,Setting,Sign 0540,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(336,1)}March, One Year Later — Kyushu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.61,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's been five years since \Nmy last visit to Hasetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.37,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This old station even \Nhas elevated tracks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.91,Phone,Sign 0554,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA376D6&}We're Rooting for You!!! \N{\c&H8C4982&}Hasetsu Native Figure Skater \N{\c&HCC714B&}Katsuki Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.00,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.07,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you skulking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,M-Minako-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.67,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, after five long years!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.13,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up straight, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.08,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:12.62,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Minako-sensei wouldn't miss any \Ninfo on me coming back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.51,Default,Locals,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.38,Default,Locals,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.77,Default,Locals,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:19.55,Default,Locals,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard any news about him \Nlately. What's he been up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:22.41,Default,Locals,0000,0000,0000,,Remember he lost a big competition last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:23.73,Default,Locals,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the Nationals?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:29.21,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everyone who cheered me on \Njust because I'm from Hasetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:30.92,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I can't explain this to each of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:33.33,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll go ahead and explain it in my head, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.10,TV,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}October: Southern Regional Championships
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.66,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The figure skating competition season \Ngenerally starts in the fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:34.87,TV,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}October: Southern Regional Championships \N{\fs18}Grand Prix: United States of America \NGrand Prix: Canada
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.04,TV,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}November: Western Japan Championships \N{\fs18}Grand Prix: China \NGrand Prix: France
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.16,TV,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}Grand Prix: China \NGrand Prix: France \NGrand Prix: Japan \NGrand Prix: Russia \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:40.21,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I lost big in the comprehensive \NGrand Prix Finals early on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.83,TV,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}Grand Prix: Russia \N{\fs20}December: Grand Prix Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.67,TV,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}Grand Prix: Russia \N{\fs20}December: Grand Prix Finals \N{\fs22}FAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:43.92,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't shake off the failure,\Nand lost again in the Nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:42.84,TV,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}Japan National Figure Skating Championships!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:43.92,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}Japan National Figure Skating Championships!! \N{\fs22}FAIL AGAIN!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.46,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make it to the Four Continents \Nor the World Championships,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:44.75,TV,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}Competing Athletes Immediately Selected: \NFour Continents Championships \NWorld Championships
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.21,TV,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}Competing Athletes Immediately Selected: \NFour Continents Championships \NWorld Championships \N{fs22}Not Selected...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.46,TV,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{fs22\an8}Not Selected... \NNot Even Entered into the Universiade......
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.30,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and now the season's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.30,TV,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}Season Ended!! \N{\fs22}Going Home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.18,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to graduate from college,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:53.05,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I ended things with my coach, \Nand my future is unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:55.33,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to come home in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.51,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:58.06,Default,Local,0000,0000,0000,,Let me shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:02.94,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,You don't lose anything by \Nshaking hands! Be polite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:07.15,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Victor Nikiforov is always nice to his fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:10.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.05,Default,Minkao,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:13.82,Default,Local,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.23,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.28,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to greet everyone in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Minako-sensei, what about your ballet class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.06,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,We're closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:25.42,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,I barely have any students these days, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:27.92,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Hasetsu's losing more and more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.80,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Hardly any kids are skating these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.30,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,You should cheer things up around here, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:39.18,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.53,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's been dying to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:47.32,WorldChampion,Sign 0746,0000,0000,0000,,World Figure Skating Championships \N{\c&H2E0EA3&}Yoyogi, Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.32,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,After the men's short program of the\NWorld Figure Skating Championships,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.07,WorldChampion,,0000,0000,0000,,World Figure Skating Championship \N{\c&H2E0EA3&}Yoyogi, Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.07,WorldChampion2,,0000,0000,0000,,Victor Nikiforov (27) in 1st After Short Program \N{\c&H135D93&}Will He Score a 5th Consecutive Win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:50.28,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Russia's Victor Nikiforov is in first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.20,Phone,Sign 0753,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30\c&H000000&}BAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:57.30,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,After the Grand Prix Finals, \Nhe won the Nationals in Russia,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.16,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the European Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.54,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He's still on a roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.01,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,The men's free program will \Nstart later today, at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:07.04,Default,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri-kun isn't in the World Championships?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.63,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't make the cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:11.67,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, he can finally come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.09,Default,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.84,Yutopia,Sign 0815,0000,0000,0000,,Hasetsu Hot Springs \NYu-topia Katsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:18.35,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroko! I brought Yuri home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:18.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we coming in the front?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.92,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Minako-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.11,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for going to get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.82,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry it's been five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.26,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,It's all good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.10,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't make it \Nto your graduation, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:34.24,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Want a pork cutlet bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.65,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you lose weight, Hiroko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:38.87,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:42.75,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Minako-senpai, you always look \Nthe same, even though you drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.93,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, I've been wondering ever \Nsince I saw you at the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:47.25,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that gut?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:50.88,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Take your clothes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! Minako-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.88,Phone,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30\c&H000000&}Nooooo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.62,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you look just like your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:08:59.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:02.25,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Toshio-san! It's no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.94,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the weight a \Nfigure skater should have!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.43,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,You always did gain weight easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:08.65,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,But what can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:11.65,Rice Bowl,Sign 0909,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1B2976&}Yu-topia Katsuki Specialty Dish \N{\c&HC7937B&}Yuri's Pork Cutlet Bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.65,Default,Sign 0909,0000,0000,0000,,Eat lots of pork cutlet bowls tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.86,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.53,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Go say hi to Vicchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:24.01,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I couldn't see you one last time, Vicchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.41,Default,YSis,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:29.67,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Mari-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to visit when things are busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:36.34,Default,YSis,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how long are you staying in Hasetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.93,Default,YSis,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help out with the hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.41,Default,YSis,0000,0000,0000,,You went to college, even though \Nyou had to study an extra year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.56,Default,YSis,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:50.56,Default,YSis,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to keep skating, \NI'll support you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:54.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I think... I need more time to think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.57,Default,YSis,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:59.32,Default,YSis,0000,0000,0000,,Well, go soak in the hot spring and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:05.57,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was born and raised in Hasetsu, Kyushu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.08,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,a castle town by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.59,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The "castle" has no historical basis and \Nis a facade with a ninja house inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.91,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Its sole source of tourism income was its \Nhot spring inns, but most went under.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:19.09,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,My family's Yu-topia Akatsuki \Nis the last one standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:23.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Man, our hot spring sure hits the spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.85,Channel,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Do Not Change Channel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.33,Default - italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Group 2 has now finished skating,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.63,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I really wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.63,Default - italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and Emil Nekola from the \NCzech Republic is in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:29.69,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,If only you'd been in it, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:29.69,Default - italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}His free program performance, \Nbefitting the season finale,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.31,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,You could've told me the \Nskaters' hotel room numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.31,Default - italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}was free of mistakes, \Nearning him a personal best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:33.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.56,Default - italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The last group has just entered the arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:37.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to be your one-man ticket \Nagency to score you tickets, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:37.24,Default - italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All eyes are on Victor Nikiforov,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.99,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! I've been supporting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.99,Default - italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}who's going for his fifth consecutive \NWorld Championship gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:43.49,TV,Sign 1041,0000,0000,0080,,Victor Nikiforov, Age 27 \N{\fs15}Winner of Four Consecutive World Figure Skating Championships
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:41.62,Default - italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He will be skating last.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:45.06,Default - italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, Honda-san, this is certainly \Nunexplored territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.28,Default - italics,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It'll really be interesting to \Nsee how far he can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.28,Default,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,What about soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.45,Default,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,Sagan Tosu's having a match right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:50.91,Default - italics,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When you watch Victor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:52.03,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I was watching skating first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:52.80,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,Sagan Tosu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.75,Default,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be working?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.98,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where are you going, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm going to practice for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:02.42,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:18.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:22.63,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Our regular hours are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:34.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Yuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:36.66,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.71,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.49,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Yu-chan"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:41.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.72,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you came to skate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.54,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:45.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I can?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:48.39,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to skate alone for now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:50.64,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:52.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:56.52,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan was my rink mate \Nand two years my senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.45,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,When we were little, \Nshe was really good at skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.37,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She was my idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.66,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,the Madonna of Ice Castle Hasetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.41,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She's still cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:11.54,Default - flashback,BoyY,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:13.67,Default - flashback,GirlY,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Yuri-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.71,Default - flashback,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of my way, fatso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:20.36,Default - flashback,GirlY,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi-kun, don't be mean to the new kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:21.90,Default - flashback,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Fatso! Fatso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.20,Default - flashback,GirlY,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:28.35,SignA,Sign 1225,0000,0000,0000,,Junior World Championships, Gold \NVictor Nikiforov \N\NSofia, Bulgaria
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.35,Default - flashback,GirlY,0000,0000,0000,,Russia's Victor Nikiforov...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:32.26,Default - flashback,GirlY,0000,0000,0000,,He won the gold in the Junior Worlds \Nwith the highest score in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:34.10,Default - flashback,GirlY,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:39.86,Default - flashback,GirlY,0000,0000,0000,,Victor would go like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.36,Default - flashback,GirlY,0000,0000,0000,,This says Victor has a poodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.85,Default - flashback,GirlY,0000,0000,0000,,His poodle's super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:45.85,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:50.69,Default - flashback,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You have a poodle now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:52.80,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I named him "Victor."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:56.37,Default - flashback,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You really like Victor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:00.75,Default - flashback,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can see you compete \Nagainst Victor soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:07.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I wanted you to see this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:10.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I've been practicing it since \Nthe competitions ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:18.01,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Last up is Victor Nikiforov from Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.52,SignA,Sign 1319,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(626,1)}Victor Nikiforov (Age 27) \NCoach: Yakov Feltsman
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:19.52,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.78,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.28,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's clear he's Russia's hero! \NThe cheers are deafening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.96,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, your favorite, Victor, is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:25.53,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}After the short program, he leads \NGiacometti, in second, by a huge margin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:25.53,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,He's not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.70,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.69,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,In this program, he has four quads planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.46,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the first quad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.76,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple Lutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.32,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Very clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.69,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,The next quad is his signature move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:05.85,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,How will it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:08.36,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple flip! He lands this one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.40,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Flying sit spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:06.88,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,The music is "Stay Close to Me."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:11.24,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Given that he has a million \Nfemale fans worldwide,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:11.24,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This program brings out a new dimension \Nin Victor Nikiforov's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.38,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,he's sure free with his charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:15.14,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,You're drinking too much, Minako-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:19.23,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple Salchow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.37,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,This would tug at the \Nheartstrings more if it were
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.01,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,a younger, more naïve man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.61,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Not a hottie like Victor, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.44,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:19.53,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,A triple Lutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:30.24,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,A triple flip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:42.86,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the last quad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:48.98,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple toe loop,\Nfollowed by a triple toe loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.53,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He's landed all his quads!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:55.19,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Now, a combination spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.65,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,That was super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.72,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect copy of Victor! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:26.94,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be depressed or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:31.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But I got bored of feeling depressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.78,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I got to thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:35.78,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get my love for skating back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:40.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could remember how it was \Nwhen I copied Victor with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan, I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:46.66,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,We now have a men's singles \Nconsecutive five-time winner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.81,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,in the World Figure Skating Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:50.67,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,The victor is Russia's Victor Nikiforov!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.34,Default - italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have in mind for next season?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.42,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:18:03.18,Default,Sisters,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.29,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Axel, Lutz, and Loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.79,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't they grown since you last saw them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.02,Default,Axel,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, you really did get fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.02,Default,Loop,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really retiring?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.14,Default,Lutz,0000,0000,0000,,You've never had a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:08.19,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:10.69,Default,Sis,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Really, really, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:11.27,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my girls are such groupies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:13.65,Default,Nishigori,0000,0000,0000,,They're all your fans, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:14.84,Default,Nishigori,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.65,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nishigori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:16.71,Default,Sis,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.66,Default,Nishigori,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're fatter than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:18.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:21.16,SignB,Sign 1820,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on Advancing to the \NGrand Prix, Skater Katsuki Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.16,Default,Nishigori,0000,0000,0000,,You can come any time to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:25.11,Default,Nishigori,0000,0000,0000,,The Nishigori family's always got your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.04,Default,Sis,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.17,Default,Sis,0000,0000,0000,,Lose weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:28.29,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,During the five years I was away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:33.04,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to ignore a lot of things \Nby focusing on skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.55,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I need
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:41.71,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I can keep skating on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.68,WorldChampion2,Sign 1846,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Victor Nikiforov (27) in 1st After Short Program \N{\c&H3BACBA&}Will He Score a 5th Consecutive Win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.46,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Here in St. Petersburg, Russia,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:53.19,Feature,Sign 1848,0000,0000,0060,,Special Feature: Rising Star in Russia \NYuri Plisetsky (Age 15)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:49.44,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,rising star Yuri Plisetsky
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.65,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,is finally gearing up in earnest to \Njoin the senior competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.71,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Under coach Yakov,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:58.05,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}the 15-year-old is about to \Njoin Victor Nikiforov in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:56.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:01.45,Default - italics,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ushering Russia into an era \Nwith two champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.70,Default - flashback,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Just retire already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.66,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The pressure's on now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:13.27,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to skate on the same \Nice as Victor again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.42,PhoneTimes,Sign 1915,0000,0000,0000,,Monday, April 10 \N\NMessage from Nishigori Takeshi \N{\fs16}Slide to View
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.45,Default,Sign 1915,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nishigori?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:18.92,Default,Sign 1915,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:23.68,Phone,Sign 1920,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}[Katsuki Yuri] Tried to Skate Victor's \NFS Program [Stay Close to Me]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.36,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:28.98,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,My kids uploaded the video, and it went viral.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:32.26,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,How could you use my account \Nwithout permission again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:34.69,Default,Lutz,0000,0000,0000,,But all the skater otaku will love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.34,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Just delete it, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:42.07,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that video?! \NIt's being retweeted everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.20,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuki-kun, do you really have \Nthe time to do things like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.16,Default,Phichit,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:50.16,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,That Japanese Yuri is an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:50.16,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Yuri! Don't slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.41,TV,Sign 2004,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(191,274)\a6}Hasetsu TV
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.17,Default - italics,Weather,0000,0000,0000,,Kyushu faces a sudden cold wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:07.76,Default - italics,Weather,0000,0000,0000,,It was to be a good day for \Nviewing cherry blossoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.12,Default - italics,Weather,0000,0000,0000,,but there was a massive snowfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:12.44,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, don't hole up in your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.29,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Help shovel snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.67,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's already April, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.03,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What's on the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I turned it off so I wouldn't get calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.05,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Vicchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:38.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He's much bigger than Vicchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Could he be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:47.05,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, isn't he just like Vicchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:50.43,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,He came with a really \Ngood-looking foreign guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:52.20,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the hot spring right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:54.73,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.11,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:09.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Vi—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:11.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Victor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.96,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, starting today, I'm your coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:24.87,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you win the Grand Prix Final.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:33.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:37.02,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He was a genius who never \Nfailed to surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:40.02,TBC,Sign 2138,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:11.24,Default,YP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:12.75,Default,YP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back to Russia!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.75,0:23:17.25,Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hasetsu's great... Come on and visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:18.12,Default,Sis,0000,0000,0000,,You can see a boob flash, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:20.00,Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:19.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, no, no, no, no!
