Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:21.77,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Second Skate:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:24.25,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Two Yuris?! Drama at Yu-topia!
